response.original_title: 劇場版ハイキュー!! ゴミ捨て場の決戦
response.overview: Shoyo Hinata joins Karasuno High's volleyball club to be like his idol, a former Karasuno player known as the 'Little Giant'. But Hinata soon learns that he must team up with his middle school nemesis, Tobio Kageyama. Their clashing styles form a surprising weapon, but can their newfound teamwork defeat their rival Nekoma High in the highly anticipated 'Dumpster Battle', the long awaited ultimate showdown between two opposing underdog teams?
response.tagline: Let's play a game that can't be repeated.
response.title: HAIKYU!! The Dumpster Battle
